<paragraph blockId="5.[813,1456,1638,1716]" pageId="5" pageNumber="72">MATERIAL EXAMINED. — Right maxilla fragment with DP2-DP3, APL-225; right M3 fragment, APL-686A; left M3 fragment, APL- 686B; right hemi-mandible with m3, APL-716; left m3, APL-687.</paragraph>
